title: Bug 118780: Expression builder shows old column name instead of alias name in data set
EB: When selecting the data set in expression builder, and double clicking on the first column name, the expected result is that the alias name should be used instead of the original name. However, the actual result is that the original name of the first column is listed below the expression builder, and the alias name appears as row["column1"] above it after double clicking the original name.
